                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        def ReaderT ( : Type u) (m : Type u Type v) ( : Type u) :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Type (max u v)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Adds the ability to access a read-only value of type to a monad. The value can be locally overridden by withReader, but it cannot be mutated.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Actions in the resulting monad are functions that take the local value as a parameter, returning ordinary actions in m.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      class MonadReaderOf ( : semiOutParam (Type u)) (m : Type u Type v) :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Type v

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Reader monads provide the ability to implicitly thread a value through a computation. The value can be read, but not written. A MonadWithReader instance additionally allows the value to be locally overridden for a sub-computation.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      In this class, is a semiOutParam, which means that it can influence the choice of instance. MonadReader provides the same operations, but requires that be inferable from m.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • read : m

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Retrieves the local value.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        class MonadReader ( : outParam (Type u)) (m : Type u Type v) :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Type v

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Reader monads provide the ability to implicitly thread a value through a computation. The value can be read, but not written. A MonadWithReader instance additionally allows the value to be locally overridden for a sub-computation.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        In this class, is an outParam, which means that it is inferred from m. MonadReaderOf provides the same operations, but allows to influence instance synthesis.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  class MonadStateOf ( : semiOutParam (Type u)) (m : Type u Type v) :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Type (max (u + 1) v)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  State monads provide a value of a given type (the state) that can be retrieved or replaced. Instances may implement these operations by passing state values around, by using a mutable reference cell (e.g. ST.Ref ), or in other ways.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  In this class, is a semiOutParam, which means that it can influence the choice of instance. MonadState provides the same operations, but requires that be inferable from m.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  The mutable state of a state monad is visible between multiple do-blocks or functions, unlike local mutable state in do-notation.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • get : m

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Retrieves the current value of the monad's mutable state.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • set : m PUnit

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Replaces the current value of the mutable state with a new one.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  • modifyGet { : Type u} : ( ) m

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Applies a function to the current state that both computes a new state and a value. The new state replaces the current state, and the value is returned.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    It is equivalent to do let (a, s) := f ( get); set s; pure a. However, using modifyGet may lead to higher performance because it doesn't add a new reference to the state value. Additional references can inhibit in-place updates of data.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Instances
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    source
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    @[reducible, inline]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    abbrev getThe ( : Type u) {m : Type u Type v} [MonadStateOf m] :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    m

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Gets the current state that has the explicitly-provided type . When the current monad has multiple state types available, this function selects one of them.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Equations
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    • getThe = MonadStateOf.get
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Instances For
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      source
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      @[reducible, inline]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      abbrev modifyThe ( : Type u) {m : Type u Type v} [MonadStateOf m] (f : ) :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      m PUnit

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Mutates the current state that has the explicitly-provided type , replacing its value with the result of applying f to it. When the current monad has multiple state types available, this function selects one of them.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      It is equivalent to do set (f ( get)). However, using modify may lead to higher performance because it doesn't add a new reference to the state value. Additional references can inhibit in-place updates of data.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Equations
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • modifyThe f = MonadStateOf.modifyGet fun (s : ) => (PUnit.unit, f s)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Applies a function to the current state that has the explicitly-provided type .                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           source
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          class MonadState ( : outParam (Type u)) (m : Type u Type v) :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Type (max (u + 1) v)

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          State monads provide a value of a given type (the state) that can be retrieved or replaced. Instances may implement these operations by passing state values around, by using a mutable reference cell (e.g. ST.Ref ), or in other ways.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          In this class, is an outParam, which means that it is inferred from m. MonadStateOf provides the same operations, but allows to influence instance synthesis.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          The mutable state of a state monad is visible between multiple do-blocks or functions, unlike local mutable state in do-notation.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          • get : m

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Retrieves the current value of the monad's mutable state.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          • set : m PUnit

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Replaces the current value of the mutable state with a new one.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          • modifyGet { : Type u} : ( ) m

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Applies a function to the current state that both computes a new state and a value. The new state replaces the current state, and the value is returned.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            It is equivalent to do let (a, s) := f ( get); set s; pure a. However, using modifyGet may lead to higher performance because it doesn't add a new reference to the state value. Additional references can inhibit in-place updates of data.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          Instances
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            source

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            m PUnit

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            It is equivalent to do set (f ( get)). However, using modify may lead to higher performance because it doesn't add a new reference to the state value. Additional references can inhibit in-place updates of data.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                inductive EStateM.Result ( : Type u) :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Type u

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                The value returned from a combined state and exception monad in which exceptions do not automatically roll back the state.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Result is equivalent to Except , but using a single combined inductive type yields a more efficient data representation.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  def EStateM ( : Type u) :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Type u

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  A combined state and exception monad in which exceptions do not automatically roll back the state.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Instances of EStateM.Backtrackable provide a way to roll back some part of the state if needed.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  EStateM is equivalent to ExceptT (StateM ), but it is more efficient.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  Equations

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              class EStateM.Backtrackable ( : outParam (Type u)) ( : Type u) :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Type u

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Exception handlers in EStateM save some part of the state, determined by , and restore it if an exception is caught. By default, is Unit, and no information is saved.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • save :

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Extracts the information in the state that should be rolled back if an exception is handled.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              • restore :

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Updates the current state with the saved information that should be rolled back. This updated state becomes the current state when an exception is handled.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Instances
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                source
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                @[inline]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                def EStateM.tryCatch { : Type u} [Backtrackable ] { : Type u} (x : EStateM ) (handle : EStateM ) :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                EStateM

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Handles exceptions thrown in the combined error and state monad.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                The Backtrackable instance is used to save a snapshot of part of the state prior to running x. If an exception is caught, the state is updated with the saved snapshot, rolling back part of the state. If no instance of Backtrackable is provided, a fallback instance in which is Unit is used, and no information is rolled back.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Equations
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                • x.tryCatch handle s = match x s with | EStateM.Result.error e s_1 => handle e (EStateM.Backtrackable.restore s_1 (EStateM.Backtrackable.save s)) | ok => ok

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    class Hashable ( : Sort u) :

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      source
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      inductive Lean.Name :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Type

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Hierarchical names consist of a sequence of components, each of which is either a string or numeric, that are written separated by dots (.).

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Hierarchical names are used to name declarations and for creating unique identifiers for free variables and metavariables.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      You can create hierarchical names using a backtick:

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      `Lean.Meta.whnf

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      It is short for .str (.str (.str .anonymous "Lean") "Meta") "whnf".

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      You can use double backticks to request Lean to statically check whether the name corresponds to a Lean declaration in scope.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      ``Lean.Meta.whnf

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      If the name is not in scope, Lean will report an error.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      There are two ways to convert a String to a Name:

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      1. Name.mkSimple creates a name with a single string component.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      2. String.toName first splits the string into its dot-separated components, and then creates a hierarchical name.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • anonymous : Name

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        The "anonymous" name.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • str (pre : Name) (str : String) : Name

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        A string name. The name Lean.Meta.run is represented at

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        .str (.str (.str .anonymous "Lean") "Meta") "run"
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      • num (pre : Name) (i : Nat) : Name

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        A numerical name. This kind of name is used, for example, to create hierarchical names for free variables and metavariables. The identifier _uniq.231 is represented as

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        .num (.str .anonymous "_uniq") 231
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Instances For
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        source
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        @[implemented_by Lean.Name.hash._override]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        noncomputable def Lean.Name.hash :
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Name UInt64

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        A hash function for names, which is stored inside the name itself as a computed field.

                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Equations
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • Lean.Name.anonymous.hash = UInt64.ofNatLT 1723 Lean.Name.hash._proof_1
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • (p.str s).hash = mixHash p.hash s.hash
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        • (p.num v).hash = mixHash p.hash (if h : v < UInt64.size then UInt64.ofNatLT v h else UInt64.ofNatLT 17 Lean.Name.hash._proof_2)
